text: Manfred Kanther (born 26 May 1939) is a German conservative politician. He was born in Schweidnitz, Silesia. He was Minister of the Interior of the Federal Republic of Germany from 1993 to 1998. He has been a member of the CDU. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Politicians of the Christian Democratic Union of Germany Category:Living people Category:Interior ministers of Germany
